🔐 Privacy Policy

Effective Date: March 26, 2026

Welcome to Ultimate Generator App 🔥 (“App”, “we”, “our”, or “us”).
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.

1. Information We Collect
a. User Input (Custom Data)

The App allows users to input custom data such as:

Names
Options for generators
Lists and preferences

Important:

This data is stored locally on your device only
We do not store, collect, or transmit this data to our servers
b. Purchase Information (RevenueCat)

If you purchase a subscription, we use RevenueCat to manage in-app purchases.

RevenueCat may collect:

Purchase status (active/inactive)
Subscription type
Anonymous identifiers

We do not receive or store your payment details.
All payments are securely handled by Google Play Billing.

c. Device Information (Limited)

We may collect limited technical data such as:

App version
Device type
Crash logs (if applicable)

This is used only to:

Improve app performance
Fix bugs
d. Advertising (if applicable)

The free version of the App may display ads.

Third-party ad providers may collect:

Device identifiers
Basic usage data

This is governed by their respective privacy policies.

2. How We Use Information

We use information only to:

Provide app functionality
Enable premium features
Improve performance and user experience

We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data.

3. Data Storage and Security
User data (e.g., lists, inputs) is stored locally on your device
We do not maintain external databases for user content
We implement reasonable security measures to protect app integrity
4. Data Sharing

We do not share your personal data, except:

With RevenueCat for subscription management
With Google Play for billing
With ad providers (if ads are enabled)

These services operate under their own privacy policies.

5. Children’s Privacy

The App is not specifically directed to children under 13.
We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

6. Your Choices

You can:

Use the App without providing personal information
Delete your data anytime by clearing app storage or uninstalling the App
Manage subscriptions via Google Play
7. Data Retention
Since data is stored locally, you control retention
We do not retain user data on external servers
8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
